Package com.onfleet.demo.homework.util

Supplies utilities involved with testing and/or executing the demo RouteCalculator homework problem for OnFleet.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DatasetSpec
    Specifies the boundaries for a sample dataset.
    FileUtil
    Small utility to quickly load packaged data files.
    NameHelper
    Utility that loads a dataset of common given- and sur-names, for use when auto-generating names.
    ObjectGenerator
    Utility object to generate instances of Driver, Location and Task for testing and execution.
    ObjectGenerator.Watermarks  
    RandomNumberUtil
    Centralized access to a shared Random number generator.
    SampleDataset
    Represents a generated (or loaded) sample dataset, comprised of Location, Driver, and Task records.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    KnownDataset
    Enumerates sample datasets that can be loaded directly from the JAR.
